{"tid":1240880,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請廣傳 請幫手 唔好再比林鄭 黑警 醫管局fake 9外國傳媒，心好累，我通頂搵呢d資訊比大家的","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:01:58.000Z","uid":264040,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"1870c23ca714c03cc3ae71b18856a7e7bdc370aa","tid":1240880,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"資料我搵曬比大家<br />\n大家只需㩒幾個制 打少少字<br />\n<br />\n我接受唔到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好多事全球人都唔知,甚至誤會左</span></strong></span><br />\n懇求大家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一齊report比外國傳媒聽</span></span></span></strong><br />\n中英文好唔好都無所謂(本人中英文都一般)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">此post底有各大傳媒link, 香港既事由真香港人交代</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n各位戰友<br />\n以下呼籲你可能覺得無用<br />\n請饒恕我唔聰明,諗到既方法有限 有更好建議請指教<br />\n連登戰友打手臥虎藏龍，高手林立懇請幫忙<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要report事件: (唔洗打曬,feel free,唔好有壓力)</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.警察夾埋醫管局擅自攞病人資料拉人<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"> 資料輕易外洩令市民同學生唔敢求醫</span>+警察擅自入各大學拉無辜學生 （唔好忘記肺癌大叔重傷被捕）</span><br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1237679/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1237679/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/aies-backdoor/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Faies-backdoor%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=36cb27d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/aies-backdoor/tech-secure/</a> (求奇搵而資料較齊既source)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2:中信圍困事件竟然無人知,黑警如同二戰納粹德軍逼猶太人入毒氣室（<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">警察要被問責)</span></span>）<br />\n請比埋呢條link佢地:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238410/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238410/page/1</a></span><br />\n(仲要一早入去鎖門， 追究黑警暴行)<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1237056/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1237056/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3:盧偉聰呃人欺騙大眾得5人暴動但法律事實係一人定罪就對於所有人要定罪 (我們不是暴動 <span style=\"color: blue;\">我地要放人</span>)</span><br />\n(而且仲 自打嘴巴話得5個人「暴動」 5個人點解仲要放150粒催淚,膠子彈同20粒布袋彈)<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238171/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238171/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4:林鄭既sor9ry中英對照不一,Fake9外國傳媒扮撤回左惡法 </span></span><br />\n我明白有人認為暫緩等於撤回<br />\n但誤導係事實<br />\n林鄭係故意disinform全球人 <br />\n(注意唔係misinform,因為佢係特登誤導,<br />\nsorry因我曾經比老師話過我錯,以防萬一提提大家)<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232717/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232717/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各大傳媒link (好多媒體都不設投稿,我已盡搵d大媒體)</span></strong></span><br />\n總中文英文新聞媒體：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chaostec.com/worldnews.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chaostec.com%2Fworldnews.htm&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=3ddbc364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chaostec.com/worldnews.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大媒體：<br />\n美國：<br />\nThe New York Times<br />\n<a href=\"https://help.nytimes.com/hc/en-us/articles/115014925288-How-to-submit-a-letter-to-the-editor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.nytimes.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F115014925288-How-to-submit-a-letter-to-the-editor&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=884f18c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://help.nytimes.com/hc/en-us/articles/1150149252